lead_paragraph: Lionel Messi scored his 50th international goal to help Argentina beat Bolivia 2-0 in a 2018 World Cup qualifier on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Messi Scores 50th Argentina Goal in 2-0 Win Over Bolivia
